snippet: The Kansas City Chiefs clinched a playoff spot for the second straight year when the Steelers scored in the closing seconds to beat the Baltimore Ravens 31-27 on Sunday....
lead_paragraph: The Kansas City Chiefs clinched a playoff spot for the second straight year when the Steelers scored in the closing seconds to beat the Baltimore Ravens 31-27 on Sunday.
